title: Japanese launch company Interstellar Technologies raises $130 million
description:
Japanese launch vehicle startup Interstellar Technologies has raised nearly $130 million to continue development of its Zero small launch vehicle.

The post Japanese launch company Interstellar Technologies raises $130 million appeared first on SpaceNews.
